captions.text: [MUSIC PLAYING]
-Hey, everyone!

I'm Mindy from Cute
Girls Hairstyles.

One of the questions
most frequently asked

by our followers is, how
do I manage my home life

and provide you guys with a
hairstyle tutorial each week?

You can imagine that with
six kids in the house,

I usually don't get
very much sleep.

And I get up really early
to get everything done.

So I decided today
might be fun to let you

guys have an inside
look at my family life

from the perspective of
Sweet Pea, the two-year-old.
[MUSIC PLAYING]

I am not going to
lie to you guys.

Sometimes finding
the time to do it

all is really
difficult, which is

why I love it when I find
resources and ideas that
can help me save time and money.

So here's the scoop,
Subaru and YouTube

have partnered
together to create
a channel called For Mom.

It's a place where you can go
and find amazing time saving

tips for daily tasks, as well as
how to look great on a budget.

And you'll even find a bunch
of my videos over there.

I really do believe
that being a mom
is the hardest job on Earth.

But at the end of the day,
when I look at my babies,

I know that it's the most
rewarding job by far.

For Mom, sponsored by
Subaru, is amazing.

And I know you guys
are going to love it.

You can find it here by
clicking on this box.

Or you could find in
the description box
below by clicking the link.

Make sure you check it out and
we will see you guys later.
Bye bye.
[MUSIC PLAYING]
